name: Til Spring - PUNKAMBIENT1
description:
PUNKAMBIENT is a collection of audiovisual pieces composed of a pixelart generative code that creates movement through the phase of the sound wave. In conjunction with an ambient music composition, I put dark aspects and musical notes that cause binaural effects, making it possible to reach a certain level of mental trance when listening with headphones.
